<item>
            <title>[LU-10269] Fixes for selective trybits</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10269</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While checking the waiting queue for inodebits lock it is needed to take into account also try_bits of new lock and locks in that queue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Another topic to solve in this ticket is the correct using of try_bits from callers and avoiding useless or trouble making cases with extra inodebits.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
